      },
      "source": [
        "# BSL Word Transformer — full pipeline in one run (Google Colab)\n",
        "\n",
        "Runs every Colab-runnable stage of the project in dissertation order:\n",
        "\n",
        "| # | Stage | Answers |\n",
        "|---|-------|--------|\n",
        "| 1 | Setup: GPU check, clone, minimal install | — |\n",
        "| 2 | Data verification (landmarks/splits ship with the repo) | — |\n",
        "| 3 | Sanity checks: overfit-one-batch + label-shuffle | leakage / pipeline health |\n",
        "| 4 | The 12-run experiment grid | RQ1, RQ2 |\n",
        "| 5 | Grid summary: mean ± std per run group | RQ1, RQ2 |\n",
        "| 6 | Evaluate best model per group on validation (top-1/5, macro-F1, confusion) | RQ1, RQ2 |\n",
        "| 7 | Learning curves + ablation reading | RQ2 |\n",
        "| 8 | Indicative latency benchmark (synthetic) | RQ3 (indicative only) |\n",
        "| 9 | Archive everything to Google Drive | backup |\n",
        "\n",
        "**Not in this notebook, by design:** the official RQ3 latency benchmark\n",
        "(must run on a consumer laptop CPU), the held-out one-shot test (waits for\n",
        "the self-recorded test set; evaluated exactly once), McNemar's test (defined\n",
        "on test-set predictions), and the webcam demo.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Before running: Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU.** Then\n",
        "Runtime > Run all. Total time on a T4: roughly 40-60 minutes."
      ],
      "id": "1Sp3scsnJG6S"
    },
