    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Ig2d3_vlJG6W"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 2. Verify the data shipped with the clone"
      ],
      "id": "Ig2d3_vlJG6W"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 4,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QUv1HSTTJG6W",
        "outputId": "499c963f-d209-4a89-b88e-71a80454f86e",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        }
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "293 cached landmark files\n",
            "224 train / 69 val clips, 50 classes, val orgs: ['corpusngt', 'deafway', 'gpnhs']\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import json\n",
        "from pathlib import Path\n",
        "\n",
        "n_npz = sum(1 for _ in Path('data/landmarks').rglob('*.npz'))\n",
        "splits = json.load(open('data/splits.json'))\n",
        "print(f'{n_npz} cached landmark files')\n",
        "print(f\"{len(splits['train'])} train / {len(splits['val'])} val clips, \"\n",
        "      f\"{len(splits['label_list'])} classes, val orgs: {splits.get('val_orgs')}\")\n",
        "assert n_npz >= 290 and len(splits['label_list']) == 50"
      ],
      "id": "QUv1HSTTJG6W"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8DW0iEWnJG6W"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 3. Sanity checks (handbook Phase 4)\n",
        "\n",
        "**Overfit-one-batch**: the model must reach ~100% accuracy on a single fixed\n",
        "batch, proving the pipeline and labels are learnable. **Label-shuffle**: with\n",
        "permuted training labels, validation accuracy must sit near chance (2% for 50\n",
        "classes); anything higher means leakage."
      ],
      "id": "8DW0iEWnJG6W"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 5,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "sSLI1SpPJG6X",
        "outputId": "8788d1d1-903a-490a-f6f8-0e5b25ff6089",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        }
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "CompletedProcess(args=['/usr/bin/python3', '-m', 'src.train', '--config', 'configs/transformer_aug_s42.yaml', '--overfit-batch', '--device', 'cuda'], returncode=0)"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 5
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import subprocess\n",
        "import sys\n",
        "\n",
        "subprocess.run(\n",
        "    [sys.executable, '-m', 'src.train', '--config',\n",
        "     'configs/transformer_aug_s42.yaml', '--overfit-batch',\n",
        "     '--device', DEVICE],\n",
        "    check=True)"
      ],
      "id": "sSLI1SpPJG6X"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 6,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "P5LO5IFqJG6X",
        "outputId": "87849e30-f583-48b6-d730-652957a98fed",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        }
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "label-shuffle best val acc: 0.0435 (chance = 0.02)\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "subprocess.run(\n",
        "    [sys.executable, '-m', 'src.train', '--config',\n",
        "     'configs/transformer_aug_s42.yaml', '--shuffle-labels',\n",
        "     '--epochs', '20', '--device', DEVICE],\n",
        "    check=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "import torch\n",
        "shuf = torch.load('results/runs/transformer_aug_s42_shufflelabels/best.pt',\n",
        "                  map_location='cpu')\n",
        "print(f\"label-shuffle best val acc: {shuf['val_acc']:.4f} (chance = 0.02)\")\n",
        "assert shuf['val_acc'] < 0.08, 'label-shuffle sits well above chance: investigate leakage!'"
      ],
      "id": "P5LO5IFqJG6X"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dpFsTGjpJG6X"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 4. The 12-run experiment grid\n",
        "\n",
        "{transformer, lstm} x {aug, noaug} x seeds {42, 43, 44}. `check=True` aborts\n",
        "the loop on the first failure. Each run writes\n",
        "`results/runs/<run_id>/` (config copy, env.txt, metrics.csv, best.pt).\n",
        "Roughly 2-4 minutes per run on a T4."
      ],
      "id": "dpFsTGjpJG6X"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 7,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "sFj_rurSJG6X",
        "outputId": "926a8ef9-2c83-470c-9314-8296081bffeb",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        }
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "12 configs: ['lstm_aug_s42', 'lstm_aug_s43', 'lstm_aug_s44', 'lstm_noaug_s42', 'lstm_noaug_s43', 'lstm_noaug_s44', 'transformer_aug_s42', 'transformer_aug_s43', 'transformer_aug_s44', 'transformer_noaug_s42', 'transformer_noaug_s43', 'transformer_noaug_s44']\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/lstm_aug_s42.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/lstm_aug_s43.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/lstm_aug_s44.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/lstm_noaug_s42.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/lstm_noaug_s43.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/lstm_noaug_s44.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/transformer_aug_s42.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/transformer_aug_s43.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/transformer_aug_s44.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/transformer_noaug_s42.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/transformer_noaug_s43.yaml =====\n",
            "\n",
            "===== configs/transformer_noaug_s44.yaml =====\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import glob\n",
        "\n",
        "configs = sorted(glob.glob('configs/*.yaml'))\n",
        "print(f'{len(configs)} configs:', [Path(c).stem for c in configs])\n",
        "\n",
        "for cfg in configs:\n",
        "    print(f'\\n===== {cfg} =====')\n",
        "    subprocess.run(\n",
        "        [sys.executable, '-m', 'src.train', '--config', cfg,\n",
        "         '--device', DEVICE],\n",
        "        check=True)"
      ],
      "id": "sFj_rurSJG6X"
    },
